| |
| | ${lines}= | Split to lines | ${result.stdout}
| | FOR | ${pattern} | IN | @{patterns}
| | | Should not contain match | ${lines} | ${pattern}
| | | ... | stdout should not contain '${pattern}' but it did:\n${result.stdout}
